Simple Wrapper to obtain IOPlatfromSerialNumber from apple IOKit written in C

this program can simply be extended to allow for other entries in IOKit

more information about available IOKit entries visit:

http://developer.apple.com/library/mac/#documentation/devicedrivers/conceptual/IOKitFundamentals/Families_Ref/Families_Ref.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP0000021-BABCCBIJ